snippet: One day after Charlie Beljan endured a panic attack, he shot a one-under-par 71 at the Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals Classic to take a two-shot lead into the final round.
abstract: Charlie Beljan, one day after suffering panic attack, takes third-round lead at Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals Classic golf tournament in Lake Buena Vista, Fla; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: One day after Charlie Beljan endured a panic attack, he shot a one-under-par 71 at the Children’s Miracle Network Hospitals Classic to take a two-shot lead into the final round.

headline.seo: Charlie Beljan Leads Children’s Miracle Classic Despite Panic Attack
